about.description:
A cross-platform implementation of the [Language Server Protocol](https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol)
providing rich cross-editing support for the [LaTeX](https://www.latex-project.org/) typesetting system.
We provide an [extension](https://github.com/latex-lsp/texlab-vscode) for [Visual Studio Code](https://code.visualstudio.com).
about.summary: An implementation of the Language Server Protocol for LaTeX

name: texlab
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "texlab" %}
{% set version = "2.2.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/latex-lsp/{{ name }}/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 313b7c230c71a0087a2a5aadbba1d8ba1a929e1e8f98b8b7553ca956fc567835

build:
  number: 0
  missing_dso_whitelist:
    - /usr/lib/libresolv.9.dylib  # [osx]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('rust') }}
    - python >=3.6  # [unix]
    - ruamel_yaml  # [unix]
  host: []
  run: []

test:
  commands:
    - texlab --version

about:
  home: https://texlab.netlify.app
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_family: GPL
